INSERT INTO `newsarticles` (`id`, `Writer`, `title`, `content`, `image`, `date_created`) VALUES
(1, 'Rowy Donker', 'Talking to the walls', 'I woke up to the sounds coming from my son Charlie''s room. \n\nI stepped out of bed and left my room, I walked trough the hallway as I reached the door I heard him talking. \n\nI knocked on the door and asked him if he was still awake, he answered to me "Yes dad I was just talking" \n\n"Charlie Who are you talking to is asked" I asked, \n\n"I am talking to the wall dad" he said. \n\nI opened the door to see him laying in his bed and just smiling at me, "Charlie it''s late go to sleep you have school tomorrow" \n\n"Okay Dad" he said as he turned around in his bed. \n\nI smiled at him and walked trough the door and walked back to my room. \n\nI laid down and fell to sleep again. \n\nI woke up to see the time was 3:20 AM, I heard the sounds of my son talking again. \n\nI walked to his room and went in, he was sitting next to the hatch in his room. \n\n"Charlie Why aren''t you sleeping" I asked \n\n"The wall woke me up dad" He said \n\n"Son the wall doesn''t talk just go to sleep" I said a little irritated. \n\nHe went to his bed and laid down to go back to sleep. \n\nAs I walked back I heard him say "Sleep well dad", I was to tired and irritated to answer. \n\nI woke up to my son standing next to my bed, \n\n"Dad are you awake?" He asked \n\n"Yes" I said with a bit of anger in my voice. \n\n"Erm...."Charlie was a bit nervous to say what he wanted \n\n"What is wrong Charlie?" I asked him \n\n"The...The wall wants to meet you dad" he said with a smile, \n\n"Meet me?"I asked. \n\nHe grabbed my hand to led me to his room, as we stopped at his door he said to me "The walls only want to talk to you". \n\nHe waited outside as I went in, I will play the game and maybe he will sleep after this. \n\n"Hello" I said, \n\nSilence.... \n\n"My name is Michael" I said. \n\nSilence aigain. \n\n"I need to go now" I told to the air. \n\nI walked out of the room to see my son looking at me, \n\n"What did he want?" Charlie asked, \n\n"He told me that you were a nice boy and that you needed to go to sleep" I lied to him. \n\nMy son looked at me and smiled \n\n"Okay then, I will go to bed" Charlie told me. \n\nI waited for him to go into his room to close the door behind him. \n\nI went to the bathroom to go to the toilet. \n\nWhen I was done I walked past my son''s room to go to my sleep, only to hear him say "Yes I love my dad he''s the coolest", \n\nI smiled and placed my ear against the door. \n\n"But now I need to go to sleep, Sleep well Wall" I heard my son say. \n\nI smiled and stepped away from the door.... \n\n"Sleep well Charlie" \n\nI stood there in the hallway shocked as the second voice reached my ears, I barged in the door. \n\nI stood there in fear... there was a man in the hatch opening,  \n\nThe figure was sitting there at the end of my son''s bed, my son safely laying there. \n\nThe figure had not seen me, so I sneaked to Charlie picked him up. \n\nAs I ran out the door I heard the most demonic voice behind me "Michael, Charlie needs to sleep!". \n\nI closed the door behind us and called the police. \n\nThey were there in a couple of seconds what felt like a eternity, \n\nI told them what happened. \n\nI led them to the door, I left I sigh of relief to know that we were safe. \n\nThe police broke down the locked door, I stood there... The room was empty. \n\nThey searched the whole room but didn''t find anyone or anything.  \n\nThe police told me there was no one there and asked me if this was some sort of joke, I assured them it wasn''t. \n\nAs the police left the scene we just went to bed and tried to get the thought out of my head, but I knew what I saw. \n\nCharlie slept in my room next to me. \n\nWe laid there next to each other. \n\n"Dad...?" He said after a while. \n\n"Yes Charlie?" I asked \n\n"Errm..., Mr.Wall doesn''t like you" he told me with a sad face. \n\nI asked him what he meant. \n\n"Mr. Wall actually hates you....." He told me \n\nI laid there in fear holding Charlie in my arms, \n\n"I don''t like Mr. Wall either" I told Charlie \n\nCharlie looked at me and nodded, he closed his eyes and fell to sleep. \n\nI was to much in shock but after a while I couldn''t stay awake and fell asleep. \n\nI woke up to the sound of my bedroom door closing, \n\nI sat up only to see the figure standing there at the end of the bed. \n\n"Go to sleep Michael.....!".', 'Room.jpg', '2016-10-26 14:08:27');

